						               													<description>Collect Point Cards by trading creature cards with other players, until you gather six (6) of a kind.  When the last Point Card is taken, the player with the highest score wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This game contains 7 types of Harry Potter creatures, each with a point card valued at a single value from 1 thru 7, and each with 6 cards for play (no point value).  Therefore, there are 42 creature cards, and 7 point cards.  The point cards themselves need to be won, and are not dealt out.  The creature cards are the ones dealt out, and that players are trading blindly (&amp;quot;2 cards&amp;quot;, for example), with other players while trying to collect a set of 6.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Along with the 42 creature cards are 3 other cards: Harry Potter, Hagrid, and a Dementor.  These add extra intrigue to the trading &amp;amp; collecting.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
